<DATE_TIME> 1999-01-22 00:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A3894 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-UNIVERSAL-LAYOFFS-LAD     01-22 0546
