<HEADLINE>
GRAND CANYON LOGGING WOULD BE 1ST FOR PARKS 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By STEVE YOZWIAK  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
