   BKN-NETS (East Rutherford, N.J.) _ N.J. Nets' daily workout. By
Chris Broussard.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-BULLS (Chicago) _ Losing Michael Jordan is one thing, but
the now defending champion Bulls don't even have enough players to
hold a workout. Today's scrimmage should be further proof of how
low the Bulls have sunk. By Ira Berkow.
</P>
<P>
   GLF-HOPE (La Quinta, Calif.) _ Third round of the Bob Hope
Classic, with Fred Funk in the lead and three others, including
John Daly, in a tie for second. By Clifton Brown.
</P>
<P>
   TEN-AUSTRALIA (Melbourne) _ The early rounds continue at the
Australian Open, with Rafter another upset victim.
</P>
