<P>
   FBN-ROMANNUMERAL _ Nothing breathes ``class'' like a Roman
numeral. ``Super Bowl 33'' would sound more like a motor oil or a
bathroom cleanser than the solemn and
</P>
<P>
   tremendous midwinter ritual it truly is, were it not elevated
and dignified with a glorious, graven Roman numeral at the end:
XXXIII. There speaks all the pomp and circumstance of the Caesars
and the Popes. There is a marble-chiseled grandeur to the event,
conferred by the Latinate tail. (Browning, Palm Beach Post). WITH
ILLUSTRATION
</P>
