   FBN-BETTINGLINE _ Betting line aside, because of heritage,
history and legacy, a Falcons' victory against Denver would rank as
one of the biggest upsets in Super Bowl history. You have to harken
back to the Jets in Super III to find that big a shocker. (Schultz,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 30.
</P>
<P>
   FBN-PRESSURE _ MIAMI _ The pressure on game day, especially for
first-time teams, can be overwhelming for Super Bowl participants.
Pre-game jitters lead to pre-game mistakes _ Thurman Thomas lost
his helmet _ that often carry into the first quarter. Some of the
top Super participants try to describe the feeling when you run
onto the field. (Wilkinson, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). Up to 50
inches.
