<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MICROSOFT23-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    KEY MICROSOFT EXECUTIVE DEFENDS GIANT'S CONDUCT
 &HT;    Moving in (f) financial and (w) Washington queues
