<P>
   WALKER-COLUMN (Undated) _ Leonard Alkins' second term as
president of the NAACP in Boston is symbolic of a restored
stability. By Adrian Walker.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; LIFESTYLE (l) &LR;
</P>
<P>
