protection since 1995, is calling it quits. Creditors refuse to
agree to a reorganization plan, so discount retailer will liquidate
145 stores Massachusetts) and lay off 20,000 workers May. By Chris
Reidy. 1000 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   OLY-SCANDAL (Geneva) _ Australian Olympic Committee chairman
reportedly offered $50,000 inducements to two African IOC members
just hours before they voted to decide which city would host the
2000 Games. By John Powers. 900 words.
</P>
<P>
   HKN-BRUINS (Boston) _ While Ray Bourque and Dmitri Khristich
