   &UR; Top center: &LR;
</P>
<P>
   IMPEACH-TRIAL (Washington) _ The first day of questions from
senators. By R.W. Apple Jr.
</P>
<P>
   (We plan to move this story by 9 p.m. ET in `w' news file.)
</P>
